FBIS4-7791 "dreeu066_s_94003" FBIS-EEU-94-066 Daily Report 5 Apr 1994 SLOVENIA Drnovsek Seeking Replacement of Labor Minister Drnovsek Seeking Replacement of Labor Minister AU0504140294 Ljubljana Radio Slovenia Network in Slovene 1330 GMT 5 Apr 94 AU0504140294 Ljubljana Radio Slovenia Network Slovene BFN [Text] In his letter to State Chamber Chairman Herman Rigelnik, Prime Minister Dr. Janez Drnovsek proposed that the State Chamber discuss relieving Jozica Puhar, minister of labor, family and social welfare of her duty and appointing Rena Klinar to that duty at its April session. In his letter to Herman Rigelnik, Prime Minister Drnovsek also said that he has no intention of withdrawing his proposal to replace Minister Puhar.
